title: Natural Birth Pack 1 Video
description:
My favorite natural birth DVDs all in one pack

1) Aiming For A Natural Birth (Australia)
2) Birth As We Know It 2006, USA, Russia
3) Birth Into Beijing - Barbara Harper Waterbirth 2000 USA
4) Birth Story by Ina May Gaskin 2012
5) Le Premier Cri - 2007 France (depicts births worldwide without comment)
6) Lennard Rignard's Infant Self Attachment (medicated vs. unmedicated, undisturbed births show differences in infant's ability to self attach to breastfeed)
7) Orgasmic Birth 2997 USA
8) The Business of Being Born 2008, USA
9) The Face Of Birth 2013 Australia
